      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah, i get that manual error is a possibility, but we've had three different teams do the audit now and they're all using the same scanner setup. it's very consistent. \n\nthe weird thing is it's always just a few units missing, never a massive amount, and it's always these specific high-value SKUs. could there be something else? like, i don't know, maybe something with how the system logs the intake vs how the physical bin is organized?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
